{"tid":2078332,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post ］［請置頂］G20國請願！簽名師召喚！","createTime":"2020-06-25T03:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T09:08:26.000Z","uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d003b2e86616e6b8b99edb9c3a47db7a8eeed8","tid":2078332,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"要人幫手，我地都要發聲先得，大家幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[全民反國安 - G20國聯署請願行動]<br />\n<br />\n國安法草案即將落實，預計有可能於下月實施。屆時，香港將失去獨立司法制度，對香港的人權及自由，本土以及各國的利益均會做成重大損害，亦對本港的營商及勞工環境構成嚴重影響，而本港作為國際城巿的地位亦岌岌可危。<br />\n<br />\n為顯示香港人民反國安法，維護人權及公義的決心，主辦單位將聯同區議員及其他本土組織收集聯署，並向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處進行馬拉松式請願，並尋求國際社會的支持，阻止中共破壞一國兩制，人權及香港司法獨立地位，協助香港維持獨立營商環境，及保障各國在港僑民福祉及商人的在港利益。<br />\n<br />\n以下為向G20國集團及台灣領事館/辦事處聯署信內容:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c%2Fedit&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f97e3f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-hLdHHs6rDQvTr-hrO9nnT7wLgaFw37Asj4gDH96s6c/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n網上聯署:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA%2Fviewform&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=12bc8d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfc3FrAKQ9C0VVAftfvjvLtAP32_qF31kkoeJNXCBfvfl1kpA/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n實體聯署表格 (請列印並邀請身邊的人簽署, 並於6月25(四)交往以下街站 (沙田小巴站, 1400-1700; 旺角  旺東橋 moko 入口, 1100-1700; 或朗豪坊雅蘭對出, 1400-1900):<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/11bGh_3y4xcNpbxHJp5QNFls0bud23axN/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F11bGh_3y4xcNpbxHJp5QNFls0bud23axN%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=6e16bd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/11bGh_3y4xcNpbxHJp5QNFls0bud23axN/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n國安法實施後，港人將面對中共的白色恐怖，言論、結社、新聞自由等基本人權將不復存在。主辦單位懇請各位港人把握機會，合力爭取。<br />\n<br />\n全民反國安，還我真香港！香港人，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n主辦 :<br />\n1) 政府非公務員職工總會<br />\n2)香港貿易推銷及採購職工會<br />\n3)香港旅遊業革新總工會<br />\n4)寵物工會<br />\n5)香港金融業職工總會<br />\n6)社會及政治組織從業員工會<br />\n7)香港調酒師工會 BMUHK<br />\n8)香港資訊科技界工會<br />\n9)香港幼兒教育工作者工會<br />\n10)香港會計手足工會<br />\n11) 香港人力資源僱員工會<br />\n12) 香港設計師工會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bgFaUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bgFaUd.jpg&h=41dfc8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgujrsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkgujrsz.jpg&h=ed4bc3af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojmxMsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojmxMsz.jpg&h=d6bd1377&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxPfKef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxPfKef.jpg&h=3c35ea1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3pr56sB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3pr56sB.jpg&h=6eca99f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92d778860a36b524c631653b89e0f11f604cc566","tid":2078332,"uid":247311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:39:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"082f3812aa656c1b71cefda4113c3add3497f214","tid":2078332,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c9bececfadbfb34ae73acc02030ddd5fd39e429","tid":2078332,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"大家幫手<img src=\"/assets/f